commit.message: Formatted with Black.
Fixed test so that it imports pyrect properly.
Removed manifest, added CHANGES notes for v0.0.4
Adding named tuples for Point, Size, and Box values.
Expanded range of Python versions that pyrect supports.
Created onRead callback, as well as the get() and set() methods. Added tox.ini.
Bump version number to 0.1.0
Changed back to lowercase for "topleft" et al. I want to match what Pygame does.
Gave topleft, topright, bottomleft, bottomright proper camelcased names.
Adding onChange callback argument and readOnly argument, and also the unit tests for these features.
Added .tox/ to .gitignore.
Making setup.py compatible with python 2 by fixing open().
Getting rid of old markdown readme, fixing tests so they can run on Python 2, correcting version-finding code in setup.py, and modernizing .gitignore.
README and pypi entry changes.
Adding sphinx documentation files.
Updating the ignore file to ignore the coverage file made by the coverage module.
Expanding test coverage
Updated ignore file
Initial commit.
Initial commit
